Project AMI - Team TheParents

This is where any documentation of peer reviews will be placed. 

If it is not code that is being reviewed or code that cannot be placed here, please create a 250-1000 word file (Word document, txt file, etc.) that explains what was done in the peer review.

Make sure that the peer review documentation is complete before committing here. Inform your respective peer reviewee to view your thoughts and suggestions on the peer review to better understand what went right and wrong.
